column2: Question
Do you approve or disapprove of the way Nathan Deal is handling his job as governor?
Do you approve or disapprove of the way Johnny Isakson is handling his job in the U.S. Senate?
In your opinion, does Senator Isakson deserve to be re-elected to the Senate, or not?

column3: No, doesNot deserve to be re-elected

You may have heard that Governor Deal vetoed Georgia's religious liberty bill. Supporters say the bill would protect people of any religion from government interference. Critics argued the bill would lead to discrimination against gays and lesbians. In your opinion, should Governor Deal have vetoed the religious liberty bill, or not?
Would you support or oppose Georgia lawmakers attempting to pass the religious liberty bill again?

Governor Deal has vetoed a bill that would have allowed anyone age 21 and older with a weapons license to carry a concealed gun in most places on college campuses. In your opinion, should Governor Deal have vetoed this bill or not?
Would you support or oppose Georgia lawmakers attempting to pass this bill again?
